title: Drawing, "Female Head, Left Profile; Decorative Motif"
description: The sharply rising line of chin to neck; dark spots on the closed upper lip; and the heavily shaded eye are the salient features in this profile view. Short curly hair frames the face to ear-level. Scrolling shapes comprise a decorative motif to the left, integrated with and larger than the profile view.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Female Head, Left Profile; Decorative Motif".
16.4 x 15 cm (6 1/2 x 5 7/8 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-8.
